{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8e91c80c1f","title":"刘结庭对重庆“反到底”派的指示","origin":"1967年9月5日红代会清华井冈山一部第三动态组编《动态》第141期。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"06a1d2d555","index":0,"year":1967,"month":9,"day":null,"articleId":"8e91c80c1f"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"cc9516e9ec","name":"重庆文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"af21de5b65","name":"刘结庭"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0fddfa05e9","type":"title","text":"刘结庭对重庆“反到底”派的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8e91c80c1f"},{"id":"59ba92b7b6","type":"authors","text":"刘结庭","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8e91c80c1f"},{"id":"9d0364ebd0","type":"paragraph","text":"一、文攻武卫主要是文攻，武卫是次要的，位置不要颠倒了，李井泉的同伙有上千人，×地的阶级斗争盖子还没有完全揭开。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8e91c80c1f"},{"id":"bf2157ba5e","type":"paragraph","text":"二、五十四军是绝对可以信赖的，对兰亦农、白斌有红五条来衡量。关于成都问题，不要把兰、白两人推向刘邓司令部去。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8e91c80c1f"},{"id":"028f068b9d","type":"paragraph","text":"三、反到底派的大方向始终是正确的。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8e91c80c1f"},{"id":"da44db2572","type":"paragraph","text":"四、“红成”在十条中肯定是革命群众组织，但最近犯有严重错误，如果继续挑起武斗，就自取灭亡。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8e91c80c1f"},{"id":"938eabab88","type":"paragraph","text":"五、造反派如果不把李井泉及其同伙揪彻底，不管新老造反派，都要人头落头。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8e91c80c1f"},{"id":"92ec039024","type":"appellation","text":"","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8e91c80c1f"}],"page":{"id":"4a4d8388a7","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8e91c80c1f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}